  "body": "it may be important to either remove the donations link or clearly state that the donations are not for the Nethermind project while we are merging the libs\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\nI think for now there is no rush with it but later we may consider things like:\r\n* making cortex repos private\r\n* using cortex repos as reusable libs for other project (may have no time / resources for it as it would require some maintenance)\r\n* using Cortex libs as NuGets for Nethermind (probably harder than maintaining monorepo)\r\n* other things?\r\n\r\n---\r\n",
